title: 59: Resorts in Charleston, SC
description:
We have some actual exciting news this episode, so listen up! Then listen to us read some ridiculous reviews written by both real and not so real people. I'm too sick/seeping too much to think of funny things to write, so just try to enjoy another exploration of awful reviews and the people who write them. 
Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/beachtoosandy for a monthly livestream Q&A!
Go watch our latest YouTube video to see us reveal the man behind the intro: youtu.be/l8Qzn-kW2wY

Buy our merch! https://store.dftba.com/collections/beach-too-sandy-water-too-wet
